No. 10-10875. Shirley Williams, Petitioner v. Michael J. Astrue, Commissioner of Social Security. 565 U.S. 932, 132 S. Ct. 374,

181 L. Ed. 2d 237,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6523, October 3, 2011.
